title: What is he talking about? (1-2 mins)
description: Short and fun! A 1-2 minute word game about what someone is talking about.
Answer.about: "Figuring out connection between stated word and images."
Answer.comment: "The questions seemed easy when there was only one image that matched the word (olives, for example).  But when the word matched 2 images, how to decide?  For hat I chose the one that had only a hat as being most direct, though one image also had hat and mittens.  Then there is the thought--maybe Bob was trying to communicate not which image had a hat, but which image needed one!!  Didn't take that choice, but I thought of it."
